5.2.4 Vent engine leak test (low pressure) 1. Verify that both shut-off valves are closed.

2. On the VCB screen:

• Energize (  ) the  Aux iliary  Press ure  Purge  valve. • Verify that the  Air Flow Valve ,  O2 Flow Valve  and the  Exhal ation  Flow Valve  are energized (  ). • Set the  Air DAC ,  O2 DAC , and the  Exh alation  DAC  counts to 60,000 (this will release all pressurized gas from the system).

3. Attach the “low-pressure test tool” to the  INSP iratory outlet.

